Base Salary: $1000.0
Work Hours: 45
Bonus: 10.0 %
Final Salary: $1100.0
2.==========
Increment denied.
3.==========
$50 Increment approved.
4.==========
5.==========
Name: Neymar
Base Salary: $1050.0
Work Hours: 85
Bonus: 10.0 %
Final Salary: $1155.0
6.==========
7.==========
Name: Messi
Base Salary: $1000.0
Work Hours: 50
Language: Java
Final Salary: $1700.0
8.==========
